Goal Representation:
Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['1. Put dish soap in the dishwasher.', '2. Wash the bowls and the plates using the dishwasher.']

behavior put_soap_in_dishwasher(dishsoap:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(dishsoap, dishwasher)
        # Place the dish soap inside the dishwasher

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishsoap: item where:
            is_soap(dishsoap)
        # Select dish soap
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher
        put_soap_in_dishwasher(dishsoap, dishwasher)

Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['Put dish soap in the dishwasher, then wash the bowls and the plates with the dishwasher.']

behavior load_dishwasher(soap:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(soap, dishwasher)
        # Put dish soap inside the dishwasher

behavior start_dishwasher(dishwasher:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(dishwasher) # Close the dishwasher door
        achieve is_on(dishwasher) # Turn on the dishwasher to wash

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind soap: item where:
            is_soap(soap)
        # Select dish soap
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher
        load_dishwasher(soap, dishwasher)
        start_dishwasher(dishwasher)
